snippet.title: Clouzy! - Official Trailer | Pax Online 2021
snippet.description:
Check out Clouzy!, an upcoming farming game where you explore the world alongside your flying pet, collect delicious fruits, and cook tasty meals to look after your cloud daycare.

Clouzy! is headed to Xbox and PC.
